</div>

  <div class="jqPuzzle">
    <%= image_tag @picture.url, :class => "jqPuzzle"%>
  </div>

  <div class="instructions">
    <p> Thank you for playing Picto Puzzler. Select from the relaxing images provided, or upload your own to play.
      <ul>
        <li> The puzzle will be automatically shuffled, and the timer will start once the first move is made. </li>
        <li> Select any tile next to the empty slot to move the pieces into place. </li>
        <li> Select the "Original" button to see the unscrambled pictures. </li>
        <li> The "Show Numbers" button can also be used for additional help. </li>
        <li> To restart the game, select "Shuffle Again." </li>
      </ul>
    </p>
  </div>



